A shattered computer monitor screen exploding outward in dramatic slow motion, glass fragments suspended mid-air catching light, revealing an empty void behind where the display once was. The scene is rendered in rich cyberpunk style with deep purple and electric blue neon lighting casting dramatic shadows. Circuit board patterns are faintly visible within the broken glass shards. A sleek silver laptop sits nearby on a reflective black desk surface, glowing warmly as an untouched alternative. The atmosphere conveys technological frustration and the allure of change, with rain-streaked windows in the background showing a moody cityscape of glowing advertisements and towering buildings.
